---
title: BBQ Steak Sandwiches with Sous Vide Potatoes and Garlic-Butter Buns
description: We've packed your favourite summer BBQ flavours into an easy sandwich supper that perfect for any season! Steak and sweet onions are slathered with smoky BBQ sauce, then sandwiched between toasty garlic-butter buns.
